nteriors\/latest-study-room-interior-design-ideas\/\">study room<\/a> is considered incomplete if ample book storage ideas don&#8217;t accompany the study table. This study table with a compact wall-mounted cabinet allows you to organise volumes conveniently so that you can quickly grab them during study time.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145841\/study-table-with-book-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Study table with wall-mounted book storage: open sectional slots for easy access and organisation\" class=\"wp-image-54798\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145841\/study-table-with-book-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145841\/study-table-with-book-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145841\/study-table-with-book-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145841\/study-table-with-book-storage-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145841\/study-table-with-book-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Use the top shelf for photo frames and trophies<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior solutions at affordable prices\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/04\/15153118\/end-to-end-home-interior-solutions-at-affordable-prices-scaled.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Modern Book Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This modern book storage is a game-changer since it looks like a &#8216;room within a room&#8217;. PVC cupboards accompany the low-lying sleeping space on one side and a wide shelf on the other side, while the entrance is framed by drawers underneath and open shelves on the remaining three sides, which also looks stylish.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145832\/modern-book-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Modern book storage consists of drawers and open shelves on three sides\" class=\"wp-image-54797\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145832\/modern-book-storage.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145832\/modern-book-storage-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145832\/modern-book-storage-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145832\/modern-book-storage-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145832\/modern-book-storage-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A perfect leisure spot for rainy evenings<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Hidden Book Storage<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This hidden book storage hack features a fixed and regular-sized wall cabinet with shelves with another duplicate wall cabinet behind it but with a slide-out mechanism. It looks dynamic, versatile and luxurious since it provides extra storage space and helps you utilise the otherwise unused corner space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/09145823\/hidden-book-storage.jpg\" alt=\"Wall cabinet with shelves concealing a hidden book storage unit features a slide-out mechanism\" class=\"wp-image-54796\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/