n\n\n\n<p>You could use either of these methods to maintain easy access to your books:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Place books for children on lower shelves in your home library.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Organise by alphabetical order (author\/title).<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Organise by specific genres or themes.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Organise by specific colour schemes.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Organise your books in your compact home by implementing one or more of these book storage ideas.&nbsp; A resourceful book storage hack is an excellent way to add a sense of creativity and sophistication to your home. It is tailored to fit the owner&#8217;s needs and preferences and helps you keep all your books in&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":54791,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":"","_wp_rev_ctl_limit":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-54788","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-home-interiors"},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>9 Clever Book Storage Ideas for a Stylish and Organized Space<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Finding clever book storage hacks for small apartments has never been easier. Check out these brilliant design and furniture ideas for some inspiration.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/book-storage-ideas\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"9 Clever Book Storage Ideas for a Stylish and Organized Space\